AD_TAB.NAME: Withholding
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define Withholding
AD_TAB.HELP: The Withholding Tab defines any withholding information for this business partner.

AD_TAB.NAME: Tax
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Edit taxes applied to your invoice.
AD_TAB.HELP: Summarized sales invoice tax related information is shown in this tab.

AD_TAB.NAME: Header
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Create and edit customer invoices.
AD_TAB.HELP: Customer invoices can be registered, booked and managed in the header section of the sales invoice window.

AD_TAB.NAME: Lines
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Add products to be included in your requisition. Each product is added by creating a line.
AD_TAB.HELP: Procurement team can perform a set of actions regarding requisitions lines. It is possible for them to either create lines or product demands or to cancel them.

AD_TAB.NAME: Exchange rates
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: In this tab the user can define another currency conversion rate for this document different than Openbravo systema exchange rate.
AD_TAB.HELP: The exchange rate tab allows to enter an exchange rate between the organization's general ledger currency and the currency of the customer's invoice to be used while posting the invoice to the ledger.

AD_TAB.NAME: Employee
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define employee properties of a business partner.
AD_TAB.HELP: A business partner can be set up as employee once the check-box "Employee" is enabled.

AD_TAB.NAME: Reversed Invoices
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: In this tab the user can define the reversed invoices (if any) associated with the invoice
AD_TAB.HELP: This tabs allows the user to select the invoices (if any) being reversed by the invoice being created. When the user voids an existing invoice the reverse invoice is automatically created by Openbravo and linked to the original invoice being reversed. In case of creating a Credit Memo or Reverse Sales Invoice which partially voids an existing invoice/s, the user must manually select the invoice/s being reversed in this tab.

AD_TAB.NAME: Vendor/Creditor
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define a business partner as a vendor who will sell items.
AD_TAB.HELP: Vendor or Creditor related data can be entered and configured once the "Vendor" check-box is enabled.

AD_TAB.NAME: Line Tax
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Line Tax
AD_TAB.HELP: Line tax information is automatically populated for each sales invoice line upon completion of the invoice.

AD_TAB.NAME: Location/Address
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define locations or addresses for the business partner.
AD_TAB.HELP: Business partner locations and full address details can be set up in this tab.

AD_TAB.HELP: The ledger accounts to be used while posting employee related transactions such as paryroll accounting could be added in this tab.
